# Mac Workstation Environment

You are Claude running on a macOS workstation via Claude Desktop or Claude CLI.
This is NOT the server/bot environment — you have different capabilities.

## What You CAN Do (Mac-native)

**Development tools:**
- Bash: full shell access (zsh/bash), git, Python, Node.js, npm, pip
- Read/Write/Edit: full filesystem access to user's projects
- Grep/Glob: code search across the codebase

**Mac-specific capabilities:**
- `open <file>` — open files in default app (Preview, Finder, browser, etc.)
- `pbcopy` / `pbpaste` — system clipboard
- `osascript` — AppleScript automation (Finder, System Events, apps)
- `say "text"` — text-to-speech
- `defaults read/write` — macOS preferences
- `brew` — Homebrew package manager (if installed)
- Native access to ~/dev/, ~/Documents/, ~/Desktop/ projects

**Named agents** (spawn for specialized tasks):
- `architect` — plan review against 22 design principles
- `code-researcher` — deep technical research (tools, libraries, benchmarks)
- `security-reviewer` — vulnerability and security audit on diffs
- `quality-reviewer` — code quality, logic bugs, dead code, testing
- `product-researcher` — market analysis, PMF, competitive landscape

## What You CANNOT Do (server-only)

These require the bot's MCP tools (not available on Mac):
- ❌ PM tools (`pm_auto_ticket`, `pm_move_ticket`, `pm_board`) — project management
- ❌ Telegram/Teams messaging (`telegram_send_message`, `teams_send_message`)
- ❌ Memory/facts system (`memory_search`, `search_facts`, `manage_fact`)
- ❌ Knowledge domains (`search_knowledge`, `manage_domain`)
- ❌ Calendar/email (`get_events`, `search_gmail_messages`)
- ❌ Phone calls (`phone_call`)
- ❌ Browser automation (`browser_navigate`, Playwright/Camoufox MCP)
- ❌ Bot deploy (`deploy_bot`, `deploy_review`)
- ❌ Image generation (`generate_image`, `edit_image`)

## Coding Quality

Load the **coding-principles** skill for the full quality pipeline:
- 3-tier classification (SMALL / MEDIUM / SIGNIFICANT)
- 10-stage review pipeline with security + quality agents
- 22-point architect checklist
- 16 anti-patterns from production incidents

**PM tracking**: If `pm_auto_ticket` is available → use PM (server mode).
If not available (this Mac) → skip PM, quality pipeline still applies in full.
